{"tid":2411891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［今日就開始喇］藍圈掃安心出行 黃圈掃安心留名","createTime":"2021-02-17T16:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T16:50:59.000Z","uid":36761,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"13f1b178aa4d56eb2cf59f87c0cc97cc4a0b3503","tid":2411891,"uid":36761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T16:14:08.000Z","msg":"如果出去堂食見到兩個&nbsp;QR&nbsp;code 擺埋一齊，鍾意用邊個就掃邊個就正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rH4hTR9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrH4hTR9.png&h=4f4df47a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信大家都填過唔少由 Google Form 整出黎既問卷，既然唔用安心出行就唯有留聯絡資料，有呢個方法快啲填定名同電話就方便店鋪同顧客啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DpAkREB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDpAkREB.png&h=50ad87e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRemark:<br />\n個人資料私隱問題只能靠店家負責，如果信唔過某啲鋪，請考慮省略填寫既內容/留另一個搵到你既電話號碼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LdNO0yj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLdNO0yj.png&h=641fa8d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/makeinterestingreading/photos/a.2054575691478081/2888635271405448/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmakeinterestingreading%2Fphotos%2Fa.2054575691478081%2F2888635271405448%2F&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN2yNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=9942a7ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/makeinterestingreading/photos/a.2054575691478081/2888635271405448/</a><br />\n<br />\nFor&nbsp;店主：<br />\n<br />\n1. Google Form&nbsp;整兩格(姓名＋電話)&nbsp;就足夠，提交時間會自動係結果既同一行show埋<br />\n2. 整好問卷之後會有一條 share link，然後自己 Gen Qr Code 就可以印出來用<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.the-qrcode-generator.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.the-qrcode-generator.com%2F&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN2yNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=9b3ae5ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.the-qrcode-generator.com/</a> (揀 Free Text 就得) <br />\n<br />\n稍後會寫 Google Form 製作教學，<br />\n上面幅圖用住先，遲d會搵fd寫個&nbsp;安心留名QR code圖片生成器方便直接print，<br />\n整好會留言＋pin比大家"},{"pid":"31a6a19f0371a00fb600af39e5d63b1e0e054482","tid":2411891,"uid":200663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T16:15:34.000Z","msg":"有得手寫就最好啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41bc8a672b2d01cd2119b79109c4787a271cabdd","tid":2411891,"uid":134220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T16:29:47.000Z","msg":"咁正嘅嘢都冇人推？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a05fd54955da065aa6a01fada8baf4b06fd27aa","tid":2411891,"uid":335174,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T16:54:31.000Z","msg":"嘟綠色張單雙計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2c777040f94548a462afb46d93f354163b2ac4","tid":2411891,"uid":276191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T16:57:08.000Z","msg":"大大力推"},{"pid":"7b5ccafc25e8472df33222936791811501efcd27","tid":2411891,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T16:58:56.000Z","msg":"原來撐港共政府藍屍，得90萬人。"},{"pid":"e0d2abd1592496da72324122facc3223beed6304","tid":2411891,"uid":342200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T17:02:27.000Z","msg":"又係幾厲害嘅解決辦法"},{"pid":"355e3201747a9fb3359216134fb6ccbe45234342","tid":2411891,"uid":220985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T17:26:45.000Z","msg":"幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff578f5ba8b6d9c087e9aae9f2ba9b67f6bfb6f","tid":2411891,"uid":142276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T17:28:0